  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/8537eb61e22269ee6f416e8f9e7060ea.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/8537eb61e22269ee6f416e8f9e7060ea.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/8537eb61e22269ee6f416e8f9e7060ea.mp4?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on a magical journey combined with fast, dynamic puzzle action!</strong></h2><br>The legendary Japanese Arcade game is back!<br>Choose your favorite character - will it be World, the Overseer of the Magical Land, the mighty Justice or the devious Black Pierrot? - and play in one of the numerous game modes available.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/98c67e9278558b22afb162ef2f5bb0ef.webp?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/4fa8fa8ca175df032e993687f6f5ca0f.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/4fa8fa8ca175df032e993687f6f5ca0f.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/4fa8fa8ca175df032e993687f6f5ca0f.mp4?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Solve diabolical puzzles or beat strong opponents in versus matches. <br>Play through an exciting adventure full of twists and turns, in Story or Path of Destiny modes.<br>Challenge your friends and the best players online.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/98c67e9278558b22afb162ef2f5bb0ef.webp?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><strong>Magical Drop VI features:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/794507b178e47dae420c2a68908dfe02.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=20 height=20 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/794507b178e47dae420c2a68908dfe02.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   15 standard playable characters and new ones added in the regular seasonal DLCs, each with their own unique story and music tracks<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/8ae70f15ad9d6e20fad0148bdb9b4e11.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=20 height=20 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/8ae70f15ad9d6e20fad0148bdb9b4e11.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   6 Solo game modes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/cb2f971b7186a5b2054fb4c6fb4447da.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=20 height=20 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/cb2f971b7186a5b2054fb4c6fb4447da.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   Local and online multiplayer modes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/5285d9b10a8ace99eaac1e7189b7532d.poster.avif?t=1726574880\" width=20 height=20 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/5285d9b10a8ace99eaac1e7189b7532d.webm?t=1726574880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   Dozens and dozens of challenges & many more surprises!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/98c67e9278558b22afb162ef2f5bb0ef.webp?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176320/extras/dad61bf9573006500c1583d7300a84a8.avif?t=1726574880\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
